"{\"uid\": \"express.co.uk-sport-othersport-1933496-Keely-Hodgkinson-Team-GB-Paris-Olympics\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"  Olympic800m champion Keely Hodgkinson was forced to swap her trainers for those of communications officer Liz Birchall before stepping onto the Stade de France podium to collect her gold medal.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 195, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 23, \"end\": 39, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Keely_Hodgkinson\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Keely Hodgkinson\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Keely_Hodgkinson\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Keely_Hodgkinson\"}, {\"begin\": 146, \"end\": 161, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Stade_de_France\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Stade de France\", \"types\": [\"Q41176\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Stade_de_France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Stade_de_France\"}, {\"begin\": 146, \"end\": 161, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Stade_de_France\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Stade de France\", \"types\": [\"Q41176\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Stade_de_France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Stade_de_France\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Hodgkinson - who became Team GB's first gold medalist in the 800m since Kelly Holmes in 2004 - is a Nike-sponsored athlete and claimed her second Olympic medal while wearing the Nike Zoom Victory 2 super shoe.\", \"from\": 197, \"to\": 406, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 197, \"end\": 207, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hodgkinson_Minerals_Area\", \"score\": 0.8835322885910917, \"rank\": 0.13182054907641758, \"text\": \"Hodgkinson\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hodgkinson_Minerals_Area\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hodgkinson_Minerals_Area\"}, {\"begin\": 269, \"end\": 281, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kelly_Holmes\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Kelly Holmes\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kelly_Holmes\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kelly_Holmes\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Team GB, however, are kitted out by Adidas with all of the athletes representing Great Britain required to wear the correct team kit on the podiums.\", \"from\": 408, \"to\": 556, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 408, \"end\": 415, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_GB\", \"score\": 0.9699347619289224, \"rank\": 0.030989805496326274, \"text\": \"Team GB\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_GB\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_GB\"}, {\"begin\": 444, \"end\": 450, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Adidas\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 9.796611665745996e-24, \"text\": \"Adidas\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Adidas\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Adidas\"}, {\"begin\": 489, \"end\": 502, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Great_Britain_at_the_Olympics\", \"score\": 0.999960948157809, \"rank\": 3.0711947745729116e-05, \"text\": \"Great Britain\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Great_Britain_at_the_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Great_Britain_at_the_Olympics\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"This led to an awkward moment for Hodgkinson as she realised that she was still wearing her Nikes just moments before climbing onto the rostrum.\", \"from\": 557, \"to\": 701, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 591, \"end\": 601, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hodgkinson_Minerals_Area\", \"score\": 0.8835322885910917, \"rank\": 0.13182054907641758, \"text\": \"Hodgkinson\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hodgkinson_Minerals_Area\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hodgkinson_Minerals_Area\"}, {\"begin\": 649, \"end\