in the medal table.\", \"from\": 976, \"to\": 1234, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1008, \"end\": 1018, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hodgkinson_Minerals_Area\", \"score\": 0.8835322885910917, \"rank\": 0.13182054907641758, \"text\": \"Hodgkinson\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hodgkinson_Minerals_Area\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hodgkinson_Minerals_Area\"}, {\"begin\": 1122, \"end\": 1129, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_GB\", \"score\": 0.9699347619289224, \"rank\": 0.030989805496326274, \"text\": \"Team GB\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_GB\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_GB\"}, {\"begin\": 1133, \"end\": 1138, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.999999999735337, \"rank\": 2.644696366108779e-10, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}, {\"begin\": 1178, \"end\": 1187, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia_national_rugby_union_team\", \"score\": 0.6585238821288429, \"rank\": 0.4911928114478444, \"text\": \"Australia\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia_national_rugby_union_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia_national_rugby_union_team\"}, {\"begin\": 1192, \"end\": 1198, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_national_rugby_union_team\", \"score\": 0.9072282796650821, \"rank\": 0.060786144479297276, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_national_rugby_union_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_national_rugby_union_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Despite heading into the final of the 800m as the clear favourite with Team USA titan Athing Mu absent from the Games altogether, Hodgkinson did not have it all her own way.\", \"from\": 1236, \"to\": 1409, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1307, \"end\": 1315, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_national_team\", \"score\": 0.9415161710730776, \"rank\": 0.05585482024595253, \"text\": \"Team USA\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_national_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_national_team\"}, {\"begin\": 1322, \"end\": 1331, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Athing_Mu\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Athing Mu\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Athing_Mu\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Athing_Mu\"}, {\"begin\": 1366, \"end\": 1376, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hodgkinson_Minerals_Area\", \"score\": 0.8835322885910917, \"rank\": 0.13182054907641758, \"text\": \"Hodgkinson\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hodgkinson_Minerals_Area\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hodgkinson_Minerals_Area\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She was pushed all the way by Kenya's Mary Moraa, who hung onto the shoulder of the Brit heading onto the second and final lap.\", \"from\": 1410, \"to\": 1537, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1440, \"end\": 1445, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kenya\", \"score\": 0.9999999781734916, \"rank\": 1.2305834653500038e-08, \"text\": \"Kenya\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kenya\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kenya\"}, {\"begin\": 1448, \"end\": 1452, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mary_II_of_England\", \"score\": 0.7819574235284708, \"rank\": 0.15194190182295, \"text\": \"Mary\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mary_II_of_England\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mary_II_of_England\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Discovery+is the new home of the Olympics.\", \"from\": 1541, \"to\": 1583, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The streamer is set to broadcast 3,800 hours of sport live from Paris.\", \"from\": 1584, \"to\": 1654, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1648, \"end\": 1653, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.999999999735337, \"rank\": 2.644696366108779e-10, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Sports fans can getDiscovery+ for \\u00a33.99a month until the end of 2024 via Amazon Prime's video channels.\", \"from\": 1656, \"to\": 1759, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1729, \"end\": 1741, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Amazon_Prime\", \"score\": 0.9956366975305249, \"rank\": 0.004382286993577717, \"text\": \"Amazon Prime\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Amazon_Prime\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Amazon_Prime\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"This also comes with anAmazon Prime 30-day free trial.\", \"from\": 1760, \"to\": 1814, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"She wasn't coming past me,\\\" Hodgkinson stated.\", \"from\": 1816, \"to\": 1863, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1845, \"end\": 1855, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hodgkinson_Minerals_Area\", \"score\": 0.8835322885910917, \"rank\": 0.13182054907641758, \"text\": \"Hodgkinson\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hodgkinson_Minerals_Area\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hodgkinson_Minerals_Area\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"You have to work out in the 800m that if you go too soon, you pay for it later.\", \"from\": 1864, \"to\": 1944, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Mary really pushed me on the back straight.\", \"from\": 1945, \"to\": 1988, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1945, \"end\": 1949, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mary_II_of_England\", \"score\": 0.7819574235284708, \"rank\": 0.15194190182295, \"text\": \"Mary\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mary_II_of_England\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mary_II_of_England\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"If I was in her position I'd have done the same.\", \"from\": 1989, \"to\": 2037, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"But she was on the outside and if you slowly wind it up, control your rhythm and energy, you still have something left in that last 100m.\", \"from\": 2039, \"to\": 2177, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I have always had that finish, natural speed.\", \"from\": 2178, \"to\": 2223, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"We use your sign-up to provide content in ways you have consented to and to improve our understanding of you.\", \"from\": 2225, \"to\": 2334, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"This may include adverts from us and 3rd parties based on our understanding.\", \"from\": 2335, \"to\": 2411, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"You can unsubscribe at any time.\", \"from\": 2412, \"to\": 2444, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Read ourPrivacy Policy  \\\"But we have maximised it.\", \"from\": 2445, \"to\": 2495, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"My technique has changed.\", \"from\": 2496, \"to\": 2521, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I am a lot stronger in my core.\", \"from\": 2522, \"to\": 2553, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It's down to fine margins, but I would now back myself in a home-straight kick with Mary.\\\"\", \"from\": 2554, \"to\": 2644, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2638, \"end\": 2642, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mary_II_of_England\", \"score\": 0.7819574235284708, \"rank\": 0.15194190182295, \"text\": \"Mary\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mary_II_of_England\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mary_II_of_England\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Hodgkinson's moment in the spotlight wasn't replicated by Team GB's other major gold hopeful, Josh Kerr.\", \"from\": 2646, \"to\": 2750, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2646, \"end\": 2656, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hodgkinson_Minerals_Area\", \"score\": 0.8835322885910917, \"rank\": 0.13182054907641758, \"text\": \"Hodgkinson\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hodgkinson_Minerals_Area\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hodgkinson_Minerals_Area\"}, {\"begin\": 2704, \"end\": 2711, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_GB\", \"score\": 0.9699347619289224, \"rank\": 0.030989805496326274, \"text\": \"Team GB\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_GB\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_GB\"}, {\"begin\": 2740, \"end\": 2744, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Josh_Lyman\", \"score\": 0.999997574743005, \"rank\": 2.110867871505559e-06, \"text\": \"Josh\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Josh_Lyman\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Josh_Lyman\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The Scot punched in a British record time and outran race favourite and arch-rival Jakob Ingebrigtsen in the 1500m final, but was unable to hold off a tremendous late kick from Cole Hocker of the USA.\", \"from\": 2751, \"to\": 2951, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2773, \"end\": 2787, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Progression_of_the_British_football_transfer_fee_record\", \"score\": 0.9302850733126843, \"rank\": 0.07493914558791766, \"text\": \"British record\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Progression_of_the_British_football_transfer_fee_record\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Progression_of_the_British_football_transfer_fee_record\"}, {\"begin\": 2834, \"end\": 2852, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jakob_Ingebrigtsen\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Jakob Ingebrigtsen\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jakob_Ingebrigtsen\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jakob_Ingeb